Devices & apps

In order to get the full benefits of mobility in the product development setting, you need devices that can run the right apps and work with engineering systems, helping your teams be more productive and effective.
Collaborate across boundaries

Ease of workflow creation and management lowers the average call handling time. A rich set of APIs and plugins provides compatibility with third-party applications. The stability of the Microsoft platform keeps the solution always up and running.
Extract insight

Microsoft BI solutions help teams turn data into insights quickly. Product design and engineering groups can work with and share large and complex data sets of any type, volume, and from any source with in-memory performance.
